---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Me - My View of the World">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">About Me</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="lead text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
          Welcome to my corner of the internet. I'm passionate about exploring the intersections of technology, privacy, and financeâ€”and how they impact our daily lives.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Why I Write</h2>
        <p>
          In a world where technology is increasingly intertwined with every aspect of our lives, I believe it's crucial to maintain a critical and independent perspective. Through this blog, I aim to share insights, raise questions, and foster meaningful discussions about the challenges and opportunities we face in the digital age.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">My Background</h2>
        <p>
          With years of experience in the tech industry and a deep interest in personal finance, I've witnessed firsthand how these domains shape our society. My writing draws from this experience, combining technical knowledge with practical insights to help readers navigate our complex digital world.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">What You'll Find Here</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-4">
          <li>In-depth analysis of privacy concerns in modern technology</li>
          <li>Practical advice on managing personal finances in the digital age</li>
          <li>Critical perspectives on emerging tech trends and their societal impact</li>
          <li>Real-world examples and case studies</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-8 mt-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Let's Connect</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">
            I'm always eager to engage in meaningful discussions and hear different perspectives. Whether you have questions, suggestions, or just want to share your thoughts, don't hesitate to reach out.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors duration-200">
            Get in Touch
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout> 